1
00:00:50,049 --> 00:00:52,469
DRAMA INI HANYA REKAAN

2
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:54,971
RAKAMAN MEMATUHI GARIS PANDUAN

3
00:01:02,979 --> 00:01:05,607
Dia tiba-tiba meracau macam orang gila.

4
00:01:05,690 --> 00:01:07,484
Dia terjatuh dan kepala dia terhantuk.

5
00:01:07,567 --> 00:01:09,694
Kemudian, dia terbongkang
di lantai dan pengsan…

6
00:01:09,778 --> 00:01:11,613
I-rang. Awak okey?

7
00:01:11,696 --> 00:01:13,073
Kenal saya tak? Siapa saya?

8
00:01:13,156 --> 00:01:14,240
Ya, kenapa?

9
00:01:15,283 --> 00:01:16,159
Bong-su.

10
00:01:16,242 --> 00:01:18,244
Saya okey, suruh mereka berhenti.

11
00:01:18,328 --> 00:01:21,414
Tak, awak tak okey.
Awak suruh panggil ambulans tadi.

12
00:01:21,915 --> 00:01:23,958
Sebab saya malu duduk di sana.

13
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:33,635
{\an8}Terima kasih.

14
00:01:34,761 --> 00:01:36,471
{\an8}I-rang, tunggulah.

15
00:01:36,554 --> 00:01:38,264
{\an8}Tapi saya tak faham.

16
00:01:38,348 --> 00:01:40,016
{\an8}Awak okey selepas jatuh begitu?

17
00:01:40,099 --> 00:01:42,352
{\an8}- Jadi, awak berlakon saja?
- Berlakon?

18
00:01:42,435 --> 00:01:45,605
{\an8}Awak tiba-tiba cakap kasar,
tuding jari ke arah defendan

19
00:01:45,688 --> 00:01:47,106
{\an8}dan cuba serang dia.

20
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:48,108
{\an8}Betulkah?

21
00:01:48,691 --> 00:01:50,318
Ya, betul.

22
00:01:50,401 --> 00:01:52,320
Awak boleh menang Oscar.

23
00:01:52,403 --> 00:01:55,073
Saya bukan berlakon!
Saya tak sedar apa-apa.

24
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:58,618
Sekejap. Awak nak ke mana
dengan sakit begitu?

25
00:01:58,701 --> 00:01:59,869
- Pejabat.
- Apa?

26
00:01:59,953 --> 00:02:02,080
Saya tak boleh terus begini.
Saya kena tamatkan.

27
00:02:02,163 --> 00:02:03,414
Tamatkan?

28
00:02:05,416 --> 00:02:07,335
Helo, paderi<i>.</i> Ini Shin I-rang.

29
00:02:07,418 --> 00:02:09,796
Maaf, tapi boleh awak datang
ke pejabat saya?

30
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:11,464
Ya, ada hal mustahak.

31
00:02:12,132 --> 00:02:13,007
Sekejap…

32
00:02:19,222 --> 00:02:20,431
Helo, mak.

33
00:02:20,515 --> 00:02:21,975
Kamu dah sampai?

34
00:02:22,058 --> 00:02:22,976
Hospital mana?

35
00:02:23,768 --> 00:02:24,978
Sebenarnya…

36
00:02:26,229 --> 00:02:29,107
Dia baru saja ke pejabat.
Saya rasa mak tak perlu risau.

37
00:02:29,732 --> 00:02:30,900
Di mana pejabat dia?

38
00:02:32,235 --> 00:02:33,236
Itu,

39
00:02:34,154 --> 00:02:35,238
saya tak tahu.

40
00:02:38,575 --> 00:02:39,617
Hospital mana?

41
00:02:39,701 --> 00:02:41,953
BILIK MAHKAMAH,
PUSAT PENGANTARAAN AWAM

42
00:02:42,036 --> 00:02:44,831
- Dia balik ke pejabat.
- Yakah?

43
00:02:46,541 --> 00:02:48,251
Maknanya dia tak cedera teruk.

44
00:02:48,751 --> 00:02:50,295
Baguslah.

45
00:02:50,378 --> 00:02:54,048
I-rang ada beri kamu kad perniagaan dia?

46
00:02:54,132 --> 00:02:55,008
Apa?

47
00:02:55,091 --> 00:02:56,718
Tak, dia cakap belum ada.

48
00:02:59,554 --> 00:03:01,097
Tumpang tanya.

49
00:03:03,349 --> 00:03:05,727
Saya ibu Peguam Shin I-rang.

50
00:03:06,436 --> 00:03:09,981
Cik tahu di mana pejabat dia?

51
00:03:10,815 --> 00:03:11,649
Ya.

52
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:14,694
Ini dia.

53
00:03:15,278 --> 00:03:16,112
Terima kasih.

54
00:03:17,614 --> 00:03:19,741
PEGUAM KANAN SHIN I-RANG

55
00:03:22,035 --> 00:03:23,161
Bangunan Okcheon?

56
00:03:29,876 --> 00:03:31,586
Shin I-rang memang gila.

57
00:03:32,128 --> 00:03:33,463
Kita boleh menang mudah.

58
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,635
Pendakwa Kim?

59
00:03:39,427 --> 00:03:40,762
Lama tak jumpa, Na-hyun.

60
00:03:40,845 --> 00:03:43,223
Kenapa awak datang
ke perbicaraan sivil, Pendakwa Kim?

61
00:03:43,306 --> 00:03:45,975
Saya datang sebab ingin tahu.

62
00:03:46,059 --> 00:03:47,185
Apa?

63
00:03:47,268 --> 00:03:48,394
Geledah dan sita?

64
00:03:51,147 --> 00:03:53,191
Okey. Saya sampai sekejap lagi.

65
00:03:55,235 --> 00:03:57,362
Awak serbu Hospital Cheongil?

66
00:03:58,112 --> 00:03:59,197
Tak perlu pun.

67
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,531
Seorang lelaki mati.

68
00:04:01,241 --> 00:04:03,743
Siasatan akan tentukan
sama ada perlu atau tak.

69
00:04:05,078 --> 00:04:05,995
Jumpa lagi, Na-hyun.

70
00:04:11,584 --> 00:04:14,087
Pendakwa itu
tak habis-habis susahkan kita.

71
00:04:16,506 --> 00:04:18,299
Saya nak cuba pujuk plaintif lagi.

72
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:21,594
Dia tak patut bertindak semberono,
tambah-tambah anak dia sakit.

73
00:04:28,476 --> 00:04:29,644
Dah cari benda itu?

74
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,104
Dah, tuan.

75
00:04:32,939 --> 00:04:35,441
PESAKIT GENGSTER SERANG DOKTOR
DAKWAAN AMALAN SALAH

76
00:04:36,484 --> 00:04:38,486
Selesaikan cepat
alang-alang ada benda ini.

77
00:04:38,569 --> 00:04:41,030
Hantar kepada wartawan
dan minta penggiat YouTube siar.

78
00:04:41,864 --> 00:04:42,699
Baik, tuan.

79
00:04:50,498 --> 00:04:52,458
Patutnya saya bakar dari dulu lagi.

80
00:04:52,542 --> 00:04:54,711
Semuanya jadi begini sebab saya lembik.

81
00:04:56,963 --> 00:04:58,965
Saya tahu ini bukan urusan saya,

82
00:04:59,048 --> 00:05:00,675
tapi kes itu macam mana?

83
00:05:01,926 --> 00:05:03,094
Saya teruskan sendiri.

84
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:06,055
Saya nak awak doakan dia

85
00:05:06,764 --> 00:05:08,683
supaya roh dia tenang.

86
00:05:09,434 --> 00:05:11,811
Kenapa tak tunggu dia datang?

87
00:05:11,894 --> 00:05:13,479
Kamu dah lama bekerja bersama.

88
00:05:14,105 --> 00:05:17,191
Saya takut dirasuk kalau jumpa dia.

89
00:05:18,026 --> 00:05:19,193
Awak pasti?

90
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:22,530
Saya nak buat sendiri.

91
00:05:34,792 --> 00:05:36,294
PESAKIT GENGSTER SERANG DOKTOR

92
00:05:48,806 --> 00:05:50,641
NAMA PUN GENGSTER. HAHA

93
00:05:50,725 --> 00:05:53,311
JI-WOO

94
00:06:09,535 --> 00:06:10,620
Apa?

95
00:06:13,998 --> 00:06:15,166
Ji-woo!

96
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:18,377
Apa jadi? Kenapa?

97
00:06:21,297 --> 00:06:24,175
KALAU DAH PENJENAYAH,
MATI SAJALAH, PADAN MUKA!

98
00:06:30,389 --> 00:06:31,307
Alamak.

99
00:06:43,528 --> 00:06:45,029
Serahkan semuanya kepada saya,

100
00:06:47,156 --> 00:06:48,157
semoga awak tenang.

101
00:06:53,621 --> 00:06:55,957
Tidak! Bukan sekarang!

102
00:07:17,061 --> 00:07:18,521
En. Shin?

103
00:07:19,647 --> 00:07:21,566
Berani kau masuk campur?

104
00:07:23,234 --> 00:07:25,111
Kau berhenti sekarang.

105
00:07:25,194 --> 00:07:27,780
Kau tahu apa?
Siapa kau nak sibuk urusan aku?

106
00:07:48,676 --> 00:07:50,094
Aku nak pergi jumpa anak aku.

107
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:53,389
Kalau kau kacau lagi, siaplah.

108
00:07:55,475 --> 00:07:57,393
Mana boleh pukul paderi begitu!

109
00:08:00,938 --> 00:08:03,900
Mak cik, berani kau pukul aku?

110
00:08:04,484 --> 00:08:05,526
Apa?

111
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:06,444
"Mak cik"?

112
00:08:07,612 --> 00:08:10,490
Penat mak bekerja
untuk besarkan dan didik kamu,

113
00:08:10,573 --> 00:08:13,367
tapi kamu panggil mak "mak cik"?

114
00:08:15,912 --> 00:08:17,079
Cakap sekali lagi.

115
00:08:17,163 --> 00:08:18,873
Cakaplah, anak tak guna.

116
00:08:19,707 --> 00:08:21,083
Lari.

117
00:08:21,667 --> 00:08:24,378
Lelaki ini bukan anak puan.

118
00:08:24,462 --> 00:08:25,963
Apa?

119
00:08:33,429 --> 00:08:34,680
Shin I-rang!

120
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:54,992
Apa…

121
00:08:55,076 --> 00:08:56,452
Apa jadi?

122
00:09:01,082 --> 00:09:01,916
Ji-woo.

123
00:09:07,672 --> 00:09:09,090
Ji-woo…

124
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,763
Jadi, maksud awak,

125
00:09:16,347 --> 00:09:19,183
azimat ini seru hantu,

126
00:09:20,184 --> 00:09:24,146
anak saya ternampak hantu itu
selepas buka firma guaman di sini,

127
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:28,109
dan hantu itu mangsa perbicaraan tadi,

128
00:09:28,192 --> 00:09:29,277
Lee Gang-pung?

129
00:09:30,278 --> 00:09:31,237
Ya.

130
00:09:37,827 --> 00:09:41,455
I-rang akan sedar balik
kalau kita bakar azimat ini?

131
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,040
Bukan sekarang.

132
00:09:43,791 --> 00:09:45,167
Dia dirasuk sekarang,

133
00:09:45,251 --> 00:09:48,087
jadi kita tak tahu apa jadi nanti.

134
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:53,342
LEE GANG-PUNG

135
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:02,893
Apa jadi?

136
00:10:09,066 --> 00:10:10,359
Tolong saya, En. Peguam.

137
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:11,485
Tak nak.

138
00:10:11,569 --> 00:10:14,322
Saya tahu awak hantu, tapi malulah sikit.

139
00:10:14,405 --> 00:10:16,365
Selepas buat begitu,
minta saya tolong lagi?

140
00:10:17,033 --> 00:10:18,326
Ini kali terakhir.

141
00:10:18,409 --> 00:10:19,744
Pergi sajalah.

142
00:10:19,827 --> 00:10:22,038
Cakap baik-baik, tak nak dengar.

143
00:10:23,497 --> 00:10:24,498
Ji-woo sakit!

144
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:36,135
Dia baca artikel kisah silam saya.

145
00:10:37,303 --> 00:10:38,304
Mesti dia terkejut.

146
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:41,140
Dia tekan perut sebab sakit sangat

147
00:10:41,223 --> 00:10:42,725
sampai dia pengsan.

148
00:10:42,808 --> 00:10:45,394
Kenapa baru nak cakap?
Patutnya cakap dari awal!

149
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,606
Aduh.

150
00:10:54,904 --> 00:10:56,113
Aduh.

151
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:08,584
Boleh pergi ke Sadang-dong?

152
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,086
- Boleh, masuklah.
- Okey.

153
00:11:14,423 --> 00:11:16,050
- Saya jalan.
- Okey.

154
00:11:36,529 --> 00:11:37,988
Yang itu! Sebelah kanan.

155
00:11:38,072 --> 00:11:41,325
- 0525 dan bintang.
- 0525, bintang.

156
00:11:44,286 --> 00:11:46,247
Sini. Di dalam bilik.

157
00:11:47,873 --> 00:11:49,083
Ji-woo.

158
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:51,460
Ji-woo! Bangun.

159
00:11:57,174 --> 00:11:58,509
Apa? Ke mana dia pergi?

160
00:12:01,345 --> 00:12:02,471
Apa jadi?

161
00:12:02,555 --> 00:12:04,181
Awak nampak teksi di sini?

162
00:12:06,976 --> 00:12:08,769
Awak memandu ke sini?

163
00:12:22,825 --> 00:12:25,828
PUSAT PERUBATAN KECEMASAN

164
00:12:35,588 --> 00:12:36,630
Tolong buka pintu.

165
00:12:46,432 --> 00:12:48,142
<i>Adik boleh dengar?</i>

166
00:13:25,554 --> 00:13:26,597
Ji-woo.

167
00:13:29,725 --> 00:13:30,684
Ji-woo.

168
00:13:33,187 --> 00:13:34,939
Perutnya tiba-tiba sakit teruk.

169
00:13:35,439 --> 00:13:36,607
Dia stabil sekarang.

170
00:13:43,239 --> 00:13:44,823
Mak dah sampai.

171
00:13:50,955 --> 00:13:51,914
Maaf.

172
00:13:52,665 --> 00:13:56,001
Saya tak tahu pula
kisah silam dia boleh bawa masalah.

173
00:13:56,585 --> 00:14:00,381
Sekarang, pihak pembelaan
akan serang perwatakan En. Lee.

174
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:02,800
Untuk lawan mereka,

175
00:14:02,883 --> 00:14:04,510
saya kena tahu tentang dia.

176
00:14:05,177 --> 00:14:07,388
Semuanya termasuk kisah silam dia.

177
00:14:09,265 --> 00:14:12,142
Saya mula kenal dia 20 tahun dulu.

178
00:14:13,018 --> 00:14:14,520
Mana nak gantung?

179
00:14:14,603 --> 00:14:15,980
Di sini.

180
00:14:16,063 --> 00:14:17,106
- Sini?
- Ya.

181
00:14:17,189 --> 00:14:18,857
<i>Saya pergi ke Penjara Cheongju</i>

182
00:14:18,941 --> 00:14:21,735
<i>dengan orang gereja</i>
<i>sebab kami buat majlis Krismas di sana.</i>

183
00:14:22,444 --> 00:14:25,781
<i>Gang-pung tolong saya hias pokok Krismas.</i>

184
00:14:28,325 --> 00:14:31,036
Dia tersilap pilih haluan
dan jadi gengster,

185
00:14:31,579 --> 00:14:33,706
tapi dia menyesal atas perbuatan dia,

186
00:14:33,789 --> 00:14:36,041
serah diri dan masuk penjara.

187
00:14:42,172 --> 00:14:44,008
{\an8}MANGSA IALAH BEKAS GENGSTER

188
00:14:49,805 --> 00:14:51,515
Saya rasa cukuplah.

189
00:14:53,142 --> 00:14:54,894
Jom pergi.

190
00:14:59,857 --> 00:15:02,234
Puan kena teman Ji-woo sekarang.

191
00:15:02,735 --> 00:15:05,529
Saya akan buat yang terbaik
dalam perbicaraan.

192
00:15:05,613 --> 00:15:06,739
Okey.

193
00:15:06,822 --> 00:15:08,532
Peguam Shin.

194
00:15:08,616 --> 00:15:09,450
Ya?

195
00:15:09,533 --> 00:15:12,161
Macam mana encik masuk ke rumah saya?

196
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:15,372
Macam mana encik tahu Ji-woo sakit?

197
00:15:16,332 --> 00:15:17,374
Saya…

198
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:21,587
Saya ke rumah puan
sebab nak minta tandatangan puan.

199
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:24,131
Kebetulan saya ternampak Ji-woo pengsan.

200
00:15:24,214 --> 00:15:25,132
Pintu…

201
00:15:26,342 --> 00:15:28,135
Pintu tak terkunci.

202
00:15:29,178 --> 00:15:32,431
Saya pun tak tahu kenapa.

203
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:36,936
Jadi,

204
00:15:37,019 --> 00:15:40,230
kenapa encik bercakap dialek lain
semasa perbicaraan?

205
00:15:45,444 --> 00:15:48,238
Sebab saya orang daerah itu.

206
00:15:49,823 --> 00:15:52,952
Dialek kampung saya tiba-tiba keluar
kalau sedang marah.

207
00:15:55,454 --> 00:15:57,289
Ji-woo keseorangan sekarang.

208
00:15:57,373 --> 00:15:58,707
Puan masuklah.

209
00:15:58,791 --> 00:16:01,418
Okey, saya masuk.

210
00:16:01,502 --> 00:16:03,295
- Ya, okey.
- Jumpa lagi.

211
00:16:06,215 --> 00:16:07,091
Begini.

212
00:16:09,802 --> 00:16:10,803
Terima kasih.

213
00:16:10,886 --> 00:16:12,930
Saya buat bukan sebab awak.

214
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:18,394
Awak duduk di sini.
Kita jumpa selepas Ji-woo sedar.

215
00:16:19,561 --> 00:16:20,896
Kita bincangkan strategi.

216
00:16:21,605 --> 00:16:22,439
Okey.

217
00:16:44,586 --> 00:16:45,546
Peguam Han.

218
00:16:50,259 --> 00:16:51,093
Peguam Han?

219
00:16:53,095 --> 00:16:53,971
Helo.

220
00:16:56,181 --> 00:16:57,516
Puan masih di sini.

221
00:16:58,517 --> 00:16:59,435
Bagaimana budak itu?

222
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:03,063
Dia masih demam, tapi stabil sekarang.

223
00:17:04,982 --> 00:17:07,359
Puan nampak pucat sikit.

224
00:17:08,193 --> 00:17:09,028
Puan okey?

225
00:17:10,487 --> 00:17:11,363
Saya okey.

226
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:19,204
Dia tak sihatkah?

227
00:17:46,648 --> 00:17:47,566
Mak, saya dah balik.

228
00:17:50,152 --> 00:17:52,988
Pukul berapa sekarang? Terkejut saya.

229
00:17:53,072 --> 00:17:54,198
Shin I-rang.

230
00:18:01,246 --> 00:18:02,664
Pandang mata mak.

231
00:18:05,417 --> 00:18:08,087
Seramnya setiap kali
mak sebut nama penuh saya.

232
00:18:09,338 --> 00:18:11,340
Saya ada buat salah lagi?

233
00:18:17,805 --> 00:18:18,639
Syukurlah.

234
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:21,725
Mak.

235
00:18:21,809 --> 00:18:23,519
Pelik pula begini.

236
00:18:23,602 --> 00:18:26,063
Kenapa tak marah saya macam biasa?

237
00:18:26,688 --> 00:18:27,731
Mana boleh.

238
00:18:28,357 --> 00:18:31,318
Mana boleh marah anak kesayangan mak.

239
00:18:31,902 --> 00:18:35,114
Tapi ada benda kita kena berkira.

240
00:18:39,451 --> 00:18:40,619
Sekejap.

241
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:43,497
PERJANJIAN SEWA KOMERSIAL

242
00:18:45,332 --> 00:18:46,500
Mak dah tahu?

243
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,293
Tak susah pun.

244
00:18:48,877 --> 00:18:51,713
Kamu buka firma guaman bawah nama sendiri.

245
00:18:51,797 --> 00:18:53,423
Nampak sangat dari mana dapat duit.

246
00:18:55,300 --> 00:18:57,052
Mak, sebenarnya…

247
00:18:57,136 --> 00:18:58,512
Tak apa.

248
00:18:58,595 --> 00:19:02,307
Alang-alang jadi begini,
mak anggap saja ini pelaburan.

249
00:19:02,975 --> 00:19:04,393
Cap jari kamu di sini.

250
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:05,310
Apa…

251
00:19:05,394 --> 00:19:07,521
SEPARUH FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG
MILIK MAK

252
00:19:07,604 --> 00:19:08,689
Separuh?

253
00:19:08,772 --> 00:19:11,525
Memang kita keluarga, tapi ini tak adil.

254
00:19:11,608 --> 00:19:13,068
Kamu nak mak dapat semuanya?

255
00:19:15,988 --> 00:19:17,364
Okey.

256
00:19:17,447 --> 00:19:19,074
Saya tak ada pad dakwat.

257
00:19:29,501 --> 00:19:30,919
PARK GYEONG-HWA
SHIN I-RANG

258
00:19:31,003 --> 00:19:32,629
Selesai.

259
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:36,175
Pejabat dekat saja,
kamu datang makan di sini.

260
00:19:36,675 --> 00:19:37,843
Memandu sekejap saja…

261
00:19:38,969 --> 00:19:40,095
Ada kereta?

262
00:19:44,141 --> 00:19:47,603
{\an8}FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

263
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:49,563
Nah.

264
00:19:50,147 --> 00:19:51,356
Minyak enjin kena tukar.

265
00:19:52,149 --> 00:19:55,319
BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

266
00:20:01,033 --> 00:20:05,037
{\an8}BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

267
00:20:10,751 --> 00:20:12,794
- Opocot, terkejut aku!
- Alamak!

268
00:20:14,755 --> 00:20:16,798
Tak bolehkah awak muncul macam biasa?

269
00:20:16,882 --> 00:20:18,717
Saya lagi terkejut.

270
00:20:19,468 --> 00:20:20,886
Nak saya ketuk pintu?

271
00:20:20,969 --> 00:20:23,931
Buka pintu dan pakai tali pinggang?

272
00:20:24,681 --> 00:20:25,891
Bertenang, I-rang.

273
00:20:26,558 --> 00:20:28,060
Dia bukan manusia.

274
00:20:30,604 --> 00:20:31,688
Oh ya,

275
00:20:32,481 --> 00:20:34,650
kita kena cari
Jururawat Oh Jin-suk, bukan?

276
00:20:35,567 --> 00:20:38,070
Orang tak percaya kalau tak ada dia.

277
00:20:39,988 --> 00:20:41,823
- Saya dah jumpa dia.
- Apa?

278
00:20:41,907 --> 00:20:43,742
Agensi detektif telefon saya.

279
00:20:45,494 --> 00:20:48,830
<i>Pn. Oh, dia janda anak satu.</i>

280
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:53,001
<i>Hidup dia susah sampai</i>
<i>apabila Lee Jeong-seok tawarkan duit,</i>

281
00:20:53,669 --> 00:20:54,920
<i>dia tak mampu tolak.</i>

282
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:56,713
Jururawat Oh Jin-suk?

283
00:21:10,435 --> 00:21:11,770
Seorang ibu rela buat…

284
00:21:14,564 --> 00:21:15,774
demi anak dia.

285
00:21:19,653 --> 00:21:20,570
Tapi betulkah

286
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:23,657
demi anak puan?

287
00:21:25,867 --> 00:21:26,827
Hai, semua.

288
00:21:33,417 --> 00:21:34,751
Kenapa? Ada apa?

289
00:21:38,088 --> 00:21:38,922
Apa jadi?

290
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:42,634
Ada apa?

291
00:21:45,345 --> 00:21:47,306
IKUT AYAH KAU MASUK PENJARA
AYAH KAU PENIPU

292
00:21:47,389 --> 00:21:49,349
BERAMBUS DARI SEKOLAH!
AYAH KAU KENA RASUK?

293
00:21:55,689 --> 00:21:56,898
AYAH I-RANG PENJENAYAH!

294
00:21:56,982 --> 00:21:58,358
<i>Saya faham sangat</i>

295
00:21:59,359 --> 00:22:01,111
<i>perasaan seorang kanak-kanak…</i>

296
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:03,071
PENDAKWA KORUP

297
00:22:03,155 --> 00:22:05,365
<i>…apabila mereka sedar</i>
<i>yang kesenangan hidup mereka</i>

298
00:22:06,491 --> 00:22:07,951
tak seindah mana.

299
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:10,245
Jun-seo tak begitu lagi.

300
00:22:13,248 --> 00:22:14,166
Dia masih kecil.

301
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:16,793
Dia tak sedar apa-apa lagi.

302
00:22:18,712 --> 00:22:19,546
Okey.

303
00:22:20,756 --> 00:22:23,550
Katakan puan boleh rahsiakan
sampai bila-bila.

304
00:22:24,593 --> 00:22:27,220
- Tapi hidup puan tenang tak?
- Dah terlambat sekarang.

305
00:22:30,265 --> 00:22:32,517
Kalau dah mati, buat apa pun tak guna.

306
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:34,478
Habis cerita.

307
00:22:34,561 --> 00:22:35,729
Cerita ini belum habis.

308
00:22:38,857 --> 00:22:40,358
Ada seorang lagi akan mati.

309
00:22:41,818 --> 00:22:43,153
Maksud encik?

310
00:22:43,737 --> 00:22:44,946
Anak En. Lee Gang-pung.

311
00:22:46,698 --> 00:22:48,033
Puan nampak dia di hospital.

312
00:22:54,122 --> 00:22:55,624
Ayah jangan lama-lama, okey?

313
00:22:55,707 --> 00:22:56,958
Saya ada ujian esok.

314
00:22:58,085 --> 00:23:00,712
Aduh, ujian itu biasa saja.

315
00:23:01,296 --> 00:23:03,090
Tak lawaklah, ayah.

316
00:23:03,173 --> 00:23:04,800
Okey, Ji-woo.

317
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:07,594
Pembedahan ayah sekejap saja.

318
00:23:08,804 --> 00:23:10,514
Semoga berjaya.

319
00:23:10,597 --> 00:23:11,598
Jangan risau.

320
00:23:14,601 --> 00:23:16,853
- Jumpa nanti.
- Jumpa lagi.

321
00:23:19,356 --> 00:23:20,982
<i>Sejak ayah dia mati,</i>

322
00:23:21,066 --> 00:23:23,985
<i>dia berkurung saja di bilik</i>
<i>dan tak makan sangat pun.</i>

323
00:23:25,487 --> 00:23:28,448
<i>Kemudian, dia pengsan</i>
<i>dan sekarang, masuk wad.</i>

324
00:23:32,911 --> 00:23:35,247
Ayah dia yang sihat mati mengejut.

325
00:23:37,165 --> 00:23:38,125
Peliklah kalau

326
00:23:39,501 --> 00:23:40,585
dia okey saja.

327
00:23:46,133 --> 00:23:47,259
Sekarang, puan dah tahu.

328
00:23:48,885 --> 00:23:49,803
Berilah keterangan.

329
00:23:51,263 --> 00:23:53,807
Puan saja yang boleh membongkarnya.

330
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:56,059
Jadi, tolonglah…

331
00:23:58,854 --> 00:24:00,230
dedahkan kebenaran.

332
00:24:04,943 --> 00:24:05,777
Saya tak boleh.

333
00:24:08,238 --> 00:24:10,574
Nanti lelaki itu apa-apakan kami.

334
00:24:14,703 --> 00:24:17,831
Apa lagi yang doktor belum beritahu saya
selain tentang Oh Jin-suk?

335
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:22,294
Manalah tahu kalau geledah dan sita itu
jumpa apa-apa yang boleh lawan kita.

336
00:24:22,878 --> 00:24:25,547
Contohnya, EMR.

337
00:24:25,630 --> 00:24:27,215
EMR.

338
00:24:27,299 --> 00:24:28,133
Apa itu?

339
00:24:28,842 --> 00:24:30,343
Rekod Perubatan Elektronik.

340
00:24:30,427 --> 00:24:32,762
Itu pelayan utama dalam sesebuah hospital.

341
00:24:32,846 --> 00:24:35,098
Semua rekod pembedahan
disimpan dalam pelayan itu.

342
00:24:36,266 --> 00:24:37,142
Doktor bius?

343
00:24:37,225 --> 00:24:39,978
<i>Ada rekod kadar degupan jantung saya</i>
<i>semasa pembedahan itu?</i>

344
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:41,354
<i>Ada.</i>

345
00:24:41,438 --> 00:24:43,648
<i>Kalau kita jumpa cakera keras itu,</i>

346
00:24:43,732 --> 00:24:46,610
<i>kita ada bukti kukuh untuk lawan</i>
<i>dakwaan doktor itu yang kononnya</i>

347
00:24:46,693 --> 00:24:48,403
<i>awak mati sebab serangan jantung.</i>

348
00:24:49,654 --> 00:24:51,698
Orang kena panggil awak Peguam Romantik.

349
00:24:51,781 --> 00:24:54,367
Entah-entah,
awak pernah belajar perubatan?

350
00:24:54,451 --> 00:24:55,368
Serba boleh.

351
00:24:55,452 --> 00:24:56,786
- Apa?
- Apa?

352
00:24:58,622 --> 00:24:59,998
Saya pun baru tahu hari ini.

353
00:25:00,916 --> 00:25:01,791
<i>En. Peguam.</i>

354
00:25:05,378 --> 00:25:07,214
Mereka serah rekod palsu kepada mahkamah.

355
00:25:08,924 --> 00:25:10,050
Encik periksa saja EMR.

356
00:25:10,884 --> 00:25:13,303
Rekod asal ada dalam komputer bilik bedah.

357
00:25:15,472 --> 00:25:17,265
Pn. Oh Jin-suk beritahu saya.

358
00:25:17,349 --> 00:25:18,808
Patutlah.

359
00:25:18,892 --> 00:25:21,102
Kita boleh menang dengan bukti itu, bukan?

360
00:25:22,062 --> 00:25:23,855
Tapi di mana bilik pelayan itu?

361
00:25:23,939 --> 00:25:25,148
Itu masalahnya.

362
00:25:25,732 --> 00:25:28,944
Apabila saya tanya hospital,
katanya mereka guna yang baharu sekarang.

363
00:25:29,027 --> 00:25:31,404
Yang baharu? Mana pelayan lama?

364
00:25:32,113 --> 00:25:33,114
Mereka jual.

365
00:25:33,198 --> 00:25:34,115
Jual?

366
00:25:34,950 --> 00:25:36,993
Jadi, saya buat laporan tanpa nama.

367
00:25:37,077 --> 00:25:39,079
Mesti pihak pendakwa
sedang siasat sekarang.

368
00:25:39,162 --> 00:25:41,331
Saya nak periksa CCTV hospital.

369
00:25:41,414 --> 00:25:44,626
Awak pula cungkil maklumat
daripada pihak pendakwa.

370
00:25:45,210 --> 00:25:46,127
Okey.

371
00:25:49,422 --> 00:25:50,715
<i>Yang saya dengar,</i>

372
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:53,677
pihak pendakwa terima
laporan tanpa nama tentang EMR.

373
00:25:54,261 --> 00:25:56,179
Sebab itu mereka mula siasat.

374
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:59,766
Kita boleh tertangkap sebab si bodoh ini.

375
00:25:59,849 --> 00:26:00,809
Apa kau cakap?

376
00:26:00,892 --> 00:26:02,894
Jaga bahasa awak, Peguam Han.

377
00:26:02,978 --> 00:26:05,605
Saya tak nak bersekongkol dengan penipu.

378
00:26:05,689 --> 00:26:07,774
Hei, kau merepek apa?

379
00:26:07,857 --> 00:26:09,359
- Han Na-hyun.
- Ya?

380
00:26:09,442 --> 00:26:10,568
Keluar dari sini.

381
00:26:12,153 --> 00:26:13,738
Saya ketuai kes ini.

382
00:26:15,365 --> 00:26:16,408
Saya tak nak ulang.

383
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:22,122
{\an8}FIRMA GUAMAN TAEBAEK

384
00:26:28,211 --> 00:26:30,213
Aduh, berani dia cakap begitu.

385
00:26:31,339 --> 00:26:32,632
Apa masalah dia?

386
00:26:36,386 --> 00:26:37,470
Aduh.

387
00:26:55,947 --> 00:26:56,990
Kenapa?

388
00:26:57,073 --> 00:26:58,325
Apa masalahnya?

389
00:27:04,956 --> 00:27:06,041
Saya faham.

390
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:09,002
Encik dah bunuh orang.
Patutlah encik tak tenang.

391
00:27:09,085 --> 00:27:10,086
Bunuh…

392
00:27:11,504 --> 00:27:14,341
Bunuh dia? Aku bunuh siapa?

393
00:27:14,424 --> 00:27:17,469
Saya cakap dengan encik baik-baik,

394
00:27:18,553 --> 00:27:19,637
tapi kita bukan kawan.

395
00:27:19,721 --> 00:27:20,555
Sekejap.

396
00:27:21,181 --> 00:27:23,266
Aku sogok jururawat macam kau suruh.

397
00:27:23,808 --> 00:27:27,187
Aku serahkan EMR kepada kau
sebab kau cakap nak uruskan.

398
00:27:29,064 --> 00:27:29,939
Aku…

399
00:27:31,399 --> 00:27:33,818
rakam perbualan kita,

400
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:35,904
encik.

401
00:27:40,450 --> 00:27:41,326
Jadi?

402
00:27:42,369 --> 00:27:43,828
Siapa nak dengar?

403
00:27:44,829 --> 00:27:46,122
Hakim?

404
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:49,834
Nak cakap encik buat silap
dan bunuh seorang lelaki,

405
00:27:49,918 --> 00:27:52,504
kemudian upah peguam untuk tutup kes?

406
00:27:52,587 --> 00:27:53,421
Tak, bukan begitu.

407
00:27:53,505 --> 00:27:54,506
Hei!

408
00:28:02,555 --> 00:28:04,641
Apabila orang selesaikan masalah kita,

409
00:28:04,724 --> 00:28:06,226
kita kena bersyukur.

410
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:10,146
Jangan pula tak sedar diri, okey?

411
00:28:18,071 --> 00:28:20,490
Kira bertuahlah Peguam Han bela encik.

412
00:28:25,203 --> 00:28:27,997
Han Na-hyun sanggup
gadai nyawa demi perbicaraan.

413
00:28:48,059 --> 00:28:49,394
KENALAN

414
00:28:49,477 --> 00:28:51,104
PENDAKWA KIM HYEON-U

415
00:28:51,187 --> 00:28:52,355
Komputer hospital?

416
00:28:54,357 --> 00:28:56,025
Kami tak servis komputer hospital.

417
00:28:56,860 --> 00:29:00,613
Jadi, ada syarikat
yang servis komputer hospital?

418
00:29:00,697 --> 00:29:01,823
Mungkin.

419
00:29:04,909 --> 00:29:05,910
Informan?

420
00:29:06,745 --> 00:29:09,372
Saya tahu awak nak cari
informan tanpa nama ini.

421
00:29:10,248 --> 00:29:12,834
Kalau dia nak beri keterangan,
kami berhak tahu siapa dia.

422
00:29:12,917 --> 00:29:14,252
Saya tak tahu siapa dia.

423
00:29:14,878 --> 00:29:17,672
Orang itu guna telefon awam
dan tak ada kamera CCTV berdekatan.

424
00:29:20,049 --> 00:29:23,470
Berdasarkan laporan,
mungkin dia orang dalam.

425
00:29:23,553 --> 00:29:26,598
Awak tak boleh agak?
Atau mungkin doktor itu cakap apa-apa.

426
00:29:27,807 --> 00:29:28,975
Tak.

427
00:29:29,058 --> 00:29:31,978
Macam-macam orang keluar masuk hospital.

428
00:29:32,061 --> 00:29:33,813
Dia kata susah nak agak.

429
00:29:37,233 --> 00:29:39,068
PENYIASAT LEE
SAYA RASA DAH JUMPA

430
00:29:39,152 --> 00:29:40,445
Sekejap.

431
00:29:44,866 --> 00:29:46,659
Saya nak ke bilik air.

432
00:29:46,743 --> 00:29:47,577
Okey.

433
00:30:08,264 --> 00:30:09,432
Kenapa?

434
00:30:10,642 --> 00:30:11,810
Telefon jatuh di tandas.

435
00:30:13,061 --> 00:30:15,063
Saya kena telefon orang.
Boleh pinjam telefon?

436
00:30:15,146 --> 00:30:15,980
Boleh.

437
00:30:30,453 --> 00:30:32,372
"Alatan Terpakai Saenara."

438
00:30:47,011 --> 00:30:48,221
EN. YANG DO-GYEONG

439
00:30:49,138 --> 00:30:50,682
Helo, Peguam Yang.

440
00:30:50,765 --> 00:30:52,308
Awak dah uruskan komputer itu?

441
00:30:52,392 --> 00:30:54,602
Ya, komputer itu akan naik kapal

442
00:30:54,686 --> 00:30:57,272
dan jumpa pemilik baharu malam ini.

443
00:30:57,856 --> 00:30:59,440
Awak dah buang cakera keras?

444
00:30:59,524 --> 00:31:01,192
Dah, saya bakar dan buang.

445
00:31:01,943 --> 00:31:04,445
Pihak pendakwa sedang siasat. Hati-hati.

446
00:31:04,529 --> 00:31:05,780
Okey, selamat tinggal.

447
00:31:11,870 --> 00:31:13,329
HOSPITAL CHEONGIL

448
00:31:13,413 --> 00:31:15,915
Bodohlah kalau aku buang
benda berharga ini.

449
00:31:18,543 --> 00:31:20,795
Kita pergi ke gudang dulu.

450
00:31:28,386 --> 00:31:29,345
Di mana kamu jumpa?

451
00:31:30,763 --> 00:31:32,473
Sumber kami hantar gambar.

452
00:31:34,142 --> 00:31:35,768
Ini gambar malam semalam.

453
00:31:36,436 --> 00:31:38,688
Saya tanya hospital.
Katanya itu mereka punya.

454
00:31:39,397 --> 00:31:40,523
Di mana tempat ini?

455
00:31:40,607 --> 00:31:42,901
Incheon, pemiliknya Cho Gi-cheol.

456
00:31:44,736 --> 00:31:45,570
Incheon.

457
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,656
Nak keluarkan waran geledah?

458
00:31:49,699 --> 00:31:51,951
Saya takut terlambat nanti.
Kita pergi sekarang.

459
00:31:56,998 --> 00:31:59,167
KOMPUTER

460
00:31:59,250 --> 00:32:00,084
En. Peguam.

461
00:32:01,127 --> 00:32:03,171
Alatan Terpakai Saenara ada komputer itu.

462
00:32:03,254 --> 00:32:05,381
- Alatan Terpakai Saenara?
- Saya nampak.

463
00:32:20,313 --> 00:32:22,523
{\an8}KANG HA-NA
PEJABAT PENDAKWA RAYA

464
00:32:29,364 --> 00:32:30,198
{\an8}KIM HAE-YEONG

465
00:32:30,281 --> 00:32:33,117
{\an8}<i>Saya lampirkan maklumat</i>
<i>Alatan Terpakai Saenara dan pemiliknya.</i>

466
00:32:33,201 --> 00:32:34,452
SEMAKAN REKOD JENAYAH

467
00:32:34,535 --> 00:32:35,703
LESEN PERNIAGAAN

468
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:43,002
Terima kasih!

469
00:32:47,298 --> 00:32:49,550
Awak tak perlu datang
sampai ke sini, I-rang.

470
00:32:50,218 --> 00:32:52,428
Saya pernah bawa watak doktor bedah

471
00:32:52,512 --> 00:32:55,056
dalam drama hujung minggu SBS,
<i>Doktor</i>, setahun lepas.

472
00:32:55,139 --> 00:32:58,810
Saya tak ada dialog,
tapi tangan saya berlumuran darah.

473
00:32:58,893 --> 00:33:00,728
Ya, saya tahu.

474
00:33:01,437 --> 00:33:02,689
Saya nak cepat tadi.

475
00:33:03,606 --> 00:33:05,817
Kami kena cari pelayan komputer

476
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:08,820
yang besar sikit daripada
komputer biasa dan ada pelekat biru.

477
00:33:08,903 --> 00:33:10,863
Okey. Jangan risau. Saya boleh cari.

478
00:33:10,947 --> 00:33:12,448
- Okey.
- Jom.

479
00:33:14,117 --> 00:33:14,993
Jom pergi.

480
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:32,844
ALATAN TERPAKAI SAENARA

481
00:33:35,221 --> 00:33:36,264
Kita dah sampai.

482
00:33:49,277 --> 00:33:50,278
Maaf…

483
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,710
Awak nak buat apa dengan itu?

484
00:34:06,544 --> 00:34:08,337
Saya rasa pekerja dah balik.

485
00:34:08,421 --> 00:34:10,673
- Jadi?
- Saya curi masuk dan ambil komputer.

486
00:34:11,799 --> 00:34:14,093
Boleh awak jaga di situ?

487
00:34:14,177 --> 00:34:15,094
Okey.

488
00:34:15,678 --> 00:34:16,804
Hei…

489
00:34:17,305 --> 00:34:18,931
Rasa tak sedap hati pula.

490
00:34:29,567 --> 00:34:30,568
Begini.

491
00:34:30,651 --> 00:34:32,070
Saya rasa awak kena hati-hati.

492
00:34:32,862 --> 00:34:35,031
Saya kenal pemiliknya.

493
00:34:35,615 --> 00:34:36,866
Awak kenal dia?

494
00:34:36,949 --> 00:34:39,535
Dulu dia bos saya,
semasa saya budak bodoh dulu.

495
00:34:40,078 --> 00:34:41,746
Maknanya, dia gengster?

496
00:34:42,663 --> 00:34:43,748
Dia ganas orangnya.

497
00:34:44,373 --> 00:34:47,085
<i>Dia belasah orang</i>
<i>yang dia tak suka sampai lembik.</i>

498
00:34:47,752 --> 00:34:49,837
<i>Dia suka nyanyi satu lagi ini.</i>

499
00:34:52,465 --> 00:34:54,634
Gengster yang kerja
eksport alatan terpakai?

500
00:34:55,885 --> 00:34:57,845
Mungkin dia dah insaf.

501
00:34:58,513 --> 00:35:00,223
Jangan harap dia nak insaf.

502
00:35:03,559 --> 00:35:06,395
Dia mula edar dadah 20 tahun lepas.

503
00:35:06,479 --> 00:35:07,772
Apa? Dadah?

504
00:35:16,072 --> 00:35:17,824
Maknanya, ini bukan gudang,

505
00:35:17,907 --> 00:35:19,659
tapi sarang sindiket dadah?

506
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:23,579
Nampak gaya, tengok pekerja dia.

507
00:35:24,205 --> 00:35:27,625
- Apa jadi?
- Siapa itu?

508
00:35:28,668 --> 00:35:30,878
Lain kali, cakap awal-awal!

509
00:35:30,962 --> 00:35:33,548
Jangan simpan maklumat penting!

510
00:35:34,132 --> 00:35:35,925
Saya memang nak cakap.

511
00:35:36,008 --> 00:35:37,677
I-rang!

512
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:40,763
Mereka macam marah saja!

513
00:35:41,430 --> 00:35:42,306
Tangkap mereka!

514
00:35:42,390 --> 00:35:43,808
Apa jadi?

515
00:35:48,187 --> 00:35:49,230
Tangkap mereka!

516
00:35:58,990 --> 00:36:00,199
Tepi.

517
00:36:06,372 --> 00:36:07,582
Dua orang tak cukup.

518
00:36:09,542 --> 00:36:10,793
- Sekejap.
- Apa?

519
00:36:10,877 --> 00:36:13,045
Awak nak ke mana, I-rang?

520
00:36:20,344 --> 00:36:21,554
Tolonglah!

521
00:36:21,637 --> 00:36:22,889
Maaf!

522
00:36:24,473 --> 00:36:27,059
I-rang, saya dah tahan sekuat mungkin!

523
00:36:27,643 --> 00:36:28,811
Bukan awak.

524
00:36:29,896 --> 00:36:30,771
Bong-su, sini.

525
00:36:47,914 --> 00:36:50,499
I-rang, awak tahan mereka.

526
00:36:50,583 --> 00:36:52,376
Saya pergi cari komputer, okey?

527
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,753
Tapi…

528
00:36:54,503 --> 00:36:55,338
Saya pun!

529
00:36:56,839 --> 00:36:59,967
Apa guna kalau jumpa?
Bukannya kita boleh lari!

530
00:37:13,397 --> 00:37:15,274
Kenapa bengap sangat malam ini?

531
00:37:15,358 --> 00:37:17,693
Masuk ikut tingkap tepi!

532
00:37:17,777 --> 00:37:18,736
- Ya, tuan!
- Tingkap!

533
00:37:18,819 --> 00:37:19,695
Masuk ikut tingkap.

534
00:37:19,779 --> 00:37:21,614
Bodoh tak boleh diajar.

535
00:37:39,465 --> 00:37:41,467
Kenapa lama sangat? Mereka dah nak masuk!

536
00:37:41,550 --> 00:37:42,802
Komputer di sini.

537
00:37:42,885 --> 00:37:44,595
Sekejap. Besar sikit. Pelekat biru.

538
00:37:44,679 --> 00:37:46,305
Besar sikit. Pelekat biru.

539
00:37:47,265 --> 00:37:48,224
Tepilah.

540
00:37:51,143 --> 00:37:54,480
Aduh. Besar sikit. Pelekat biru.

541
00:37:58,401 --> 00:37:59,610
Pelekat biru.

542
00:37:59,694 --> 00:38:00,778
Saya jumpa!

543
00:38:04,448 --> 00:38:07,451
I-rang, saya jumpa komputer itu,

544
00:38:07,535 --> 00:38:08,828
tapi tak ada cakera keras!

545
00:38:09,412 --> 00:38:10,913
Itu tak penting!

546
00:38:11,747 --> 00:38:13,499
Cari jalan keluar cepat!

547
00:38:34,145 --> 00:38:35,354
Saya jumpa!

548
00:38:35,438 --> 00:38:37,023
Saya jumpa di sini.

549
00:38:37,106 --> 00:38:37,940
Yakah?

550
00:38:44,572 --> 00:38:46,073
Mana komputernya?

551
00:38:46,949 --> 00:38:49,368
Komputer? Tak, saya jumpa jalan keluar.

552
00:38:50,786 --> 00:38:52,121
Apa?

553
00:38:52,872 --> 00:38:54,874
Awak kata jangan simpan maklumat penting.

554
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,918
Kita sedang cari komputer sekarang!

555
00:38:58,627 --> 00:39:00,880
Sebutlah komputer
atau jalan keluar, hantu!

556
00:39:00,963 --> 00:39:02,673
Hantu?

557
00:39:07,803 --> 00:39:08,637
Jalan keluar.

558
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:15,770
Mana mereka?

559
00:39:15,853 --> 00:39:17,146
Jom. Cepat.

560
00:39:51,472 --> 00:39:53,015
Saya dari Pejabat Pendakwa.

561
00:39:55,351 --> 00:39:56,394
Perempuan itu…

562
00:39:56,936 --> 00:39:59,146
Saya dengar encik simpan bukti penting.

563
00:39:59,730 --> 00:40:01,524
KANG HA-NA
PEJABAT PENDAKWA RAYA

564
00:40:01,607 --> 00:40:04,151
Itu lesen buat sendirikah?

565
00:40:05,736 --> 00:40:08,364
Dia kata dia pendakwa.

566
00:40:11,158 --> 00:40:12,243
Cho Gi-cheol.

567
00:40:12,326 --> 00:40:15,329
Encik lahir pada 11 Februari 1979.

568
00:40:15,413 --> 00:40:17,373
Asal dari Sasaeng-dong, Chungcheongnam-do.

569
00:40:18,082 --> 00:40:20,626
Ibu encik mati dan ayah encik hilang.

570
00:40:20,709 --> 00:40:23,087
Tujuh sabitan serangan
dan dua sabitan penipuan.

571
00:40:24,797 --> 00:40:26,173
Encik dah tak ada harapan.

572
00:40:27,091 --> 00:40:28,008
Apa?

573
00:40:29,427 --> 00:40:31,595
Apa kau kata?

574
00:40:33,848 --> 00:40:36,934
Encik serang saya dan menghalang siasatan.

575
00:40:37,518 --> 00:40:39,353
Ditambah menyembunyikan bukti penting,

576
00:40:40,229 --> 00:40:42,022
lama encik masuk penjara nanti.

577
00:40:43,190 --> 00:40:45,192
Boleh tahan banyak jenayah encik.

578
00:40:53,159 --> 00:40:54,452
Okey, kau boleh masuk.

579
00:40:57,329 --> 00:40:58,247
Hei, buka pintu.

580
00:41:09,008 --> 00:41:10,885
Peguam Han datang nak cari

581
00:41:11,802 --> 00:41:13,637
apa yang doktor itu sembunyikan?

582
00:41:13,721 --> 00:41:15,347
Tapi dia peguam doktor itu?

583
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:21,854
Ya. Pelik juga.

584
00:41:25,191 --> 00:41:26,984
Ini Grandeur kotak 1991.

585
00:41:27,568 --> 00:41:30,446
Dalamannya pun yang asal.

586
00:41:31,572 --> 00:41:32,698
Ini kereta Cho Gi-cheol.

587
00:41:32,781 --> 00:41:35,159
Ada ruang rahsia di bawah tempat duduk.

588
00:41:36,368 --> 00:41:37,203
Ruang rahsia?

589
00:41:38,037 --> 00:41:39,079
Apa? Awak kata apa?

590
00:41:42,166 --> 00:41:44,793
I-rang! Awak buat apa?

591
00:41:45,294 --> 00:41:47,129
I-rang, jangan buat begitu.

592
00:41:47,713 --> 00:41:48,923
Aduh.

593
00:41:49,006 --> 00:41:50,549
Jangan cari pasal.

594
00:41:50,633 --> 00:41:51,717
Awak nak buat apa?

595
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:53,511
Saya jumpa.

596
00:41:53,594 --> 00:41:55,179
Biar betul?

597
00:41:55,262 --> 00:41:57,431
Mana awak tahu ada di situ?

598
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:01,685
Ini rahsia peguam.

599
00:42:02,478 --> 00:42:04,146
Apa? Seramnya.

600
00:42:04,230 --> 00:42:05,814
Okey, kita kena pergi.

601
00:42:07,149 --> 00:42:08,025
Sekejap.

602
00:42:15,824 --> 00:42:16,909
Dadah betul.

603
00:42:46,647 --> 00:42:50,943
Aduh. Terkantoi pula. Apa aku nak buat?

604
00:42:52,069 --> 00:42:53,070
Tangkap dia.

605
00:42:53,153 --> 00:42:54,530
Pihak pendakwa tahu

606
00:42:55,281 --> 00:42:56,407
saya ke sini.

607
00:42:56,490 --> 00:42:59,535
Peduli apa pendakwa atau tak. Tangkap dia.

608
00:43:25,686 --> 00:43:26,729
Apa?

609
00:43:27,479 --> 00:43:28,731
Itu kereta aku?

610
00:43:43,412 --> 00:43:45,372
Peguam Han. Puan okey?

611
00:43:46,373 --> 00:43:47,207
Habislah aku.

612
00:43:47,958 --> 00:43:48,792
Peguam?

613
00:43:49,835 --> 00:43:50,669
Bukan pendakwa?

614
00:43:51,629 --> 00:43:53,213
Kau pendakwa atau peguam?

615
00:43:54,590 --> 00:43:56,759
I-rang!

616
00:43:58,761 --> 00:44:00,054
Apa?

617
00:44:00,638 --> 00:44:03,015
Apa kamu semua nak buat di sini?

618
00:44:03,557 --> 00:44:04,391
Hei!

619
00:44:05,726 --> 00:44:07,227
Tangkap mereka semua.

620
00:44:08,520 --> 00:44:09,563
I-rang.

621
00:44:27,665 --> 00:44:28,540
Sekejap.

622
00:44:31,835 --> 00:44:32,836
Tunggu sekejap!

623
00:44:36,423 --> 00:44:38,842
Sesiapa saja di atas, aku tahu kau nampak!

624
00:44:39,343 --> 00:44:41,387
Tolong aku sekali lagi!

625
00:44:41,470 --> 00:44:44,181
Beri aku kekuatan sekali ini saja!

626
00:44:51,563 --> 00:44:54,233
Kenapa kamu tak bakar saja tempat ini?

627
00:44:54,316 --> 00:44:56,485
Kenapa nak buat sepah?

628
00:44:56,568 --> 00:44:57,528
Kamu memang

629
00:44:59,113 --> 00:45:02,074
nak susahkan aku!

630
00:45:02,866 --> 00:45:03,742
Aduh.

631
00:45:04,368 --> 00:45:05,828
Mainkan lagu.

632
00:45:05,911 --> 00:45:06,829
Ya, tuan.

633
00:45:21,135 --> 00:45:23,137
Letakkan kayu itu sebelum kau menyesal.

634
00:45:26,515 --> 00:45:27,349
Tak nak.

635
00:45:28,392 --> 00:45:31,437
Siapa patut aku pukul dulu?

636
00:45:31,520 --> 00:45:34,523
Siapa dulu yang kena?

637
00:45:36,150 --> 00:45:37,067
Okey,

638
00:45:37,609 --> 00:45:38,861
mangsa pertama,

639
00:45:39,653 --> 00:45:40,654
penipu ini.

640
00:45:44,741 --> 00:45:45,617
Awak okey?

641
00:45:48,412 --> 00:45:49,663
Ini tak adil.

642
00:45:50,831 --> 00:45:52,082
Aku datang dulu.

643
00:45:52,583 --> 00:45:54,209
Aku yang kena pukul dulu, bukan?

644
00:45:55,752 --> 00:45:57,713
Kau nak kena pukul dulu?

645
00:45:58,213 --> 00:46:01,550
Okey, kalau kau nak sangat kena pukul.

646
00:46:02,801 --> 00:46:05,512
Kuatkan lagi lagu!

647
00:46:05,596 --> 00:46:08,932
Kau nak duduk diam saja?
Orang kata kau baik sangat!

648
00:46:09,433 --> 00:46:12,060
Kau suka duduk dan tengok saja?

649
00:46:13,061 --> 00:46:14,021
Tolonglah!

650
00:46:24,364 --> 00:46:25,282
Lagu ini…

651
00:46:27,493 --> 00:46:30,287
Ini saat gembira. <i>Happy days.</i>

652
00:46:31,079 --> 00:46:32,915
Senyum sikit. Jangan masam sangat.

653
00:46:33,999 --> 00:46:35,834
Ini hari bergembira!

654
00:46:37,461 --> 00:46:39,087
<i>Apabila jumpa orang yang dibenci,</i>

655
00:46:39,171 --> 00:46:41,215
<i>atau sesuatu yang timbulkan kemarahan,</i>

656
00:46:42,007 --> 00:46:43,550
<i>kemungkinan dirasuk meningkat.</i>

657
00:47:01,568 --> 00:47:03,195
Merahnya pipi kau.

658
00:47:08,325 --> 00:47:09,409
Dah puas ayun?

659
00:47:10,035 --> 00:47:11,036
Aku pula sekarang?

660
00:47:11,787 --> 00:47:14,248
Kenapa rasa macam pernah alami?

661
00:47:15,374 --> 00:47:16,250
Kau siapa?

662
00:47:16,333 --> 00:47:17,251
Aku?

663
00:47:18,919 --> 00:47:21,755
Aku peguam gengster, Lee Gang-pung!

664
00:47:23,298 --> 00:47:24,716
Kau merepek apa?

665
00:47:26,051 --> 00:47:26,927
Jangan cari pasal.

666
00:47:27,761 --> 00:47:29,888
Mereka gengster, pengedar dadah.

667
00:47:30,931 --> 00:47:32,349
Jangan risau, cik adik.

668
00:47:32,933 --> 00:47:34,434
Nanti abang selamatkan cik adik.

669
00:47:34,518 --> 00:47:35,811
Okey?

670
00:47:37,646 --> 00:47:38,897
"Cik adik"?

671
00:47:38,981 --> 00:47:42,609
Aduh, tak cukup satu hospital
selepas aku belasah kamu semua.

672
00:47:42,693 --> 00:47:44,695
Tak apa, kubur kosong banyak lagi.

673
00:47:44,778 --> 00:47:47,573
Cakap macam tak sedar diri…

674
00:47:49,116 --> 00:47:50,075
Apa?

675
00:47:50,576 --> 00:47:51,910
Kau nak pukul nyamuk?

676
00:48:06,550 --> 00:48:08,468
Apa? Kamu nak pergi mana?

677
00:48:09,636 --> 00:48:11,179
Cepat! Pukul dia!

678
00:48:14,850 --> 00:48:17,102
Biar betul?

679
00:48:26,778 --> 00:48:28,614
I-rang!

680
00:48:28,697 --> 00:48:30,824
Tunggu. Jangan tinggalkan kami!

681
00:48:30,907 --> 00:48:31,992
Jangan!

682
00:48:34,620 --> 00:48:36,496
Sudah, jangan!

683
00:49:01,688 --> 00:49:02,522
Matilah kau!

684
00:49:19,956 --> 00:49:20,874
Apa…

685
00:49:22,959 --> 00:49:24,044
Tolak!

686
00:49:31,009 --> 00:49:32,177
Aduh.

687
00:49:47,693 --> 00:49:49,277
Pukul dia. Cepat!

688
00:50:10,549 --> 00:50:11,842
Kasihanilah daku!

689
00:50:20,892 --> 00:50:21,935
Tak nak.

690
00:50:22,436 --> 00:50:25,397
ALATAN TERPAKAI SAENARA

691
00:50:44,833 --> 00:50:47,043
I-rang!

692
00:50:47,586 --> 00:50:50,088
Aduh. Boleh puan duduk dengan dia?

693
00:50:50,172 --> 00:50:51,381
Saya nak panggil orang.

694
00:50:54,217 --> 00:50:55,051
En. Shin.

695
00:50:55,802 --> 00:50:58,180
Peguam Shin. Encik dengar?

696
00:50:58,847 --> 00:50:59,681
Peguam Shin!

697
00:51:07,439 --> 00:51:09,816
{\an8}HOSPITAL CHEONGIL

698
00:51:32,464 --> 00:51:34,090
<i>Peguam Han. Puan okey?</i>

699
00:51:47,938 --> 00:51:48,855
Encik okey?

700
00:51:50,816 --> 00:51:51,858
Ini tak adil.

701
00:51:53,026 --> 00:51:54,694
Aku datang dulu.

702
00:51:54,778 --> 00:51:56,613
Aku yang kena pukul dulu, bukan?

703
00:52:06,331 --> 00:52:08,333
{\an8}JABATAN PENDAKWAAN

704
00:52:10,919 --> 00:52:12,170
- Masuk.
- Ya, tuan.

705
00:52:12,671 --> 00:52:14,339
Cari rakaman CCTV dulu.

706
00:52:14,422 --> 00:52:15,298
Ya, tuan.

707
00:52:18,510 --> 00:52:22,180
<i>Mendiang yang dikecam</i>
<i>kerana konon menjadi mangsa</i>

708
00:52:22,264 --> 00:52:25,767
<i>ternyata dibunuh</i>
<i>oleh doktor yang membedahnya.</i>

709
00:52:25,851 --> 00:52:29,020
{\an8}<i>Pihak polis membuktikan</i>
<i>pembunuhan doktor itu</i>

710
00:52:29,104 --> 00:52:31,982
<i>berdasarkan cakera keras komputer hospital</i>

711
00:52:32,065 --> 00:52:34,734
<i>dan keterangan jururawat saksi.</i>

712
00:52:34,818 --> 00:52:35,819
<i>Sementara itu, mereka…</i>

713
00:52:47,914 --> 00:52:49,666
{\an8}TAEKWONDO HORANG

714
00:52:54,588 --> 00:52:58,592
HAN SO-HYUN

715
00:53:01,678 --> 00:53:04,598
MAHKAMAH KOREA

716
00:53:07,976 --> 00:53:08,935
USAHA MEMBUKA JALAN

717
00:53:09,019 --> 00:53:10,478
PEGUAM SEO IN-GYU DIGELAR "RAJA"

718
00:53:16,359 --> 00:53:18,194
{\an8}PEGUAM PILIHAN RAMAI!
DIPERCAYAI SEMUA!

719
00:53:18,278 --> 00:53:19,487
{\an8}AKU NAK JADI PEGUAM!

720
00:53:19,571 --> 00:53:20,614
MESTI SENTIASA MENANG!

721
00:53:25,744 --> 00:53:26,578
MENANG

722
00:53:27,329 --> 00:53:29,539
{\an8}MENANG

723
00:53:32,667 --> 00:53:35,420
{\an8}MENANG

724
00:54:06,534 --> 00:54:10,956
{\an8}KALAH

725
00:54:12,207 --> 00:54:13,416
- En. Peguam.
- Helo.

726
00:54:22,217 --> 00:54:23,259
Ji-woo macam mana?

727
00:54:47,659 --> 00:54:48,910
Hai, Ji-woo.

728
00:54:50,537 --> 00:54:52,455
Pak cik Peguam Shin I-rang.

729
00:54:53,415 --> 00:54:56,418
Kita jumpa sekejap di hospital, ingat tak?

730
00:55:00,547 --> 00:55:01,381
Kamu masih…

731
00:55:02,924 --> 00:55:04,384
tak boleh terima?

732
00:55:17,272 --> 00:55:18,106
Ji-woo.

733
00:55:20,442 --> 00:55:21,651
Ayah kamu…

734
00:55:23,945 --> 00:55:25,905
mati bukan disebabkan kamu.

735
00:55:27,866 --> 00:55:29,617
Itu bukan salah kamu.

736
00:55:31,369 --> 00:55:33,997
Janganlah salahkan diri sendiri lagi.

737
00:55:36,541 --> 00:55:38,501
Pak cik tahu apa?

738
00:55:45,216 --> 00:55:46,092
Ayah…

739
00:55:48,219 --> 00:55:49,596
tahu.

740
00:55:53,141 --> 00:55:54,642
Apa? Kamu tak suka?

741
00:55:54,726 --> 00:55:56,561
Kenapa main dengan makanan begitu?

742
00:55:57,187 --> 00:55:58,354
Tak ada apa-apa.

743
00:55:58,438 --> 00:56:01,107
Yakah? Ayah tahu ada sesuatu.

744
00:56:01,608 --> 00:56:03,068
Beritahulah ayah.

745
00:56:03,651 --> 00:56:05,779
Saya tak boleh tidur
sebab ayah berdengkur kuat.

746
00:56:06,404 --> 00:56:07,322
Aduhai.

747
00:56:07,864 --> 00:56:11,076
Habislah anak ayah tak boleh membesar
dan belajar kalau tak cukup tidur.

748
00:56:11,159 --> 00:56:14,245
Ini tak boleh jadi.
Ayah pergi jumpa doktor sekarang.

749
00:56:15,455 --> 00:56:16,998
Ini semua salah saya.

750
00:56:19,542 --> 00:56:21,586
Saya dengar berdengkur itu tak sihat,

751
00:56:23,171 --> 00:56:26,216
dan saya tahu ayah
sanggup buat saja demi saya.

752
00:56:28,176 --> 00:56:30,470
Kalau saya tak cakap begitu,

753
00:56:31,721 --> 00:56:33,515
dia takkan mati.

754
00:56:37,185 --> 00:56:38,478
Tak, Ji-woo.

755
00:56:41,314 --> 00:56:42,732
Ayah mati…

756
00:56:44,734 --> 00:56:46,694
memang bukan salah kamu.

757
00:56:48,029 --> 00:56:49,864
Hospital dan doktor yang bersalah.

758
00:56:50,615 --> 00:56:54,077
Mereka yang bersalah dah dihukum.

759
00:56:54,160 --> 00:56:55,078
Jadi…

760
00:56:58,248 --> 00:56:59,707
So Ji-woo, tolonglah…

761
00:57:01,626 --> 00:57:02,627
tolonglah ceria

762
00:57:04,129 --> 00:57:05,505
macam dulu balik.

763
00:57:07,674 --> 00:57:08,967
Hidup bahagia…

764
00:57:10,969 --> 00:57:13,388
dengan mak kamu demi ayah, okey?

765
00:57:15,849 --> 00:57:17,016
Okey, sayang?

766
00:57:20,645 --> 00:57:21,646
Ayah?

767
00:57:43,126 --> 00:57:44,043
Mak.

768
00:57:45,378 --> 00:57:47,046
Saya dengar suara ayah.

769
00:57:47,130 --> 00:57:47,964
Apa?

770
00:57:50,592 --> 00:57:54,262
Ayah kamu sentiasa ada di sisi kamu.

771
00:57:59,225 --> 00:58:02,645
Tabahkan diri

772
00:58:02,729 --> 00:58:05,023
dan hidup bahagia, okey?

773
00:58:40,099 --> 00:58:41,142
Sekejap.

774
00:58:43,228 --> 00:58:46,147
Perlukah kita bakar azimat ini?

775
00:58:50,026 --> 00:58:52,529
Dia boleh tinggal di sini.

776
00:58:52,612 --> 00:58:56,199
Dia boleh tengok Ji-woo membesar
dan tolong Min-ju.

777
00:58:56,282 --> 00:58:57,116
Peguam Shin.

778
00:58:57,200 --> 00:58:58,660
Kenapa dia kena pergi?

779
00:58:59,410 --> 00:59:00,495
Saya patut pergi.

780
00:59:01,621 --> 00:59:03,414
Ini bukan tempat saya.

781
00:59:11,172 --> 00:59:14,008
Terima kasih banyak atas semuanya.

782
00:59:21,266 --> 00:59:22,308
Sama-sama.

783
00:59:24,352 --> 00:59:25,311
Terima kasih.

784
00:59:29,857 --> 00:59:31,359
Walaupun sekejap saja,

785
00:59:32,944 --> 00:59:34,195
saya gembira.

786
00:59:36,614 --> 00:59:37,865
Saya jamin

787
00:59:39,325 --> 00:59:41,578
awak akan ke tempat yang lebih baik.

788
00:59:44,956 --> 00:59:45,999
Selamat jalan.

789
01:01:35,942 --> 01:01:38,945
BANGUNAN OKCHEON

790
01:01:43,991 --> 01:01:45,910
- Dah habis semuanya?
- Dah.

791
01:01:45,993 --> 01:01:48,663
Anak puan ada di dalam. Masuklah.

792
01:01:49,372 --> 01:01:50,915
Paderi.

793
01:01:50,998 --> 01:01:51,833
Ya?

794
01:01:51,916 --> 01:01:53,960
Terima kasih banyak.

795
01:01:54,836 --> 01:01:55,795
Tak apa.

796
01:01:57,130 --> 01:01:57,964
Saya pergi.

797
01:02:06,264 --> 01:02:09,267
{\an8}PERMOHONAN KERJA
NAMA: SHIN I-RANG

798
01:02:14,105 --> 01:02:15,314
Kamu sibuk?

799
01:02:17,483 --> 01:02:18,818
Kenapa mak datang?

800
01:02:20,403 --> 01:02:24,782
Kasihan anak mak sibuk jadi peguam
sampai tak sempat makan.

801
01:02:29,620 --> 01:02:30,538
Mak,

802
01:02:31,205 --> 01:02:32,915
pasal ayah…

803
01:02:36,419 --> 01:02:37,336
Kenapa dengan ayah?

804
01:02:40,423 --> 01:02:42,133
Tak ada apa.

805
01:02:43,593 --> 01:02:44,594
Apa ini?

806
01:02:48,347 --> 01:02:49,182
Mak,

807
01:02:50,099 --> 01:02:52,226
apabila kita sampai di hospital,

808
01:02:53,644 --> 01:02:55,438
ayah dah mati.

809
01:02:57,857 --> 01:02:59,150
Saya tertanya-tanya

810
01:03:00,067 --> 01:03:02,278
kalau dia sebenarnya nak cakap apa-apa.

811
01:03:04,447 --> 01:03:05,948
Kalau sempat cakap,

812
01:03:07,700 --> 01:03:11,579
mungkin kehilangan dia tak terasa sangat.

813
01:03:15,541 --> 01:03:16,876
Sudahlah.

814
01:03:22,423 --> 01:03:23,341
Ya,

815
01:03:24,258 --> 01:03:26,344
mungkin ada baiknya
kalau dia sempat cakap.

816
01:03:28,971 --> 01:03:31,974
Mak pun ada banyak nak tanya dia.

817
01:03:38,272 --> 01:03:39,774
Makanlah, nanti sejuk.

818
01:03:39,857 --> 01:03:41,108
Jangan balik lewat sangat.

819
01:03:41,818 --> 01:03:42,693
Balik dulu.

820
01:03:43,361 --> 01:03:44,403
Mak dah nak balik?

821
01:04:04,173 --> 01:04:07,677
FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

822
01:04:50,636 --> 01:04:55,141
FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

823
01:05:10,531 --> 01:05:11,407
Okey.

824
01:05:12,283 --> 01:05:14,827
Kita lupakan kisah silam.

825
01:05:14,911 --> 01:05:16,329
Mulakan hidup baharu.

826
01:05:22,168 --> 01:05:23,419
Kalau begini,

827
01:05:23,502 --> 01:05:26,756
bukan setakat hantu muda,
hantu tua pun takut.

828
01:05:28,591 --> 01:05:30,009
{\an8}RUNDINGAN DAN NASIHAT GUAMAN

829
01:06:16,722 --> 01:06:19,016
Adik, boleh pak cik tolong?

830
01:06:24,063 --> 01:06:26,148
Adik, ada apa ke sini?

831
01:06:31,529 --> 01:06:33,030
Pak cik

832
01:06:34,031 --> 01:06:35,324
boleh nampak saya?

833
01:06:35,950 --> 01:06:36,826
Apa?

834
01:06:52,508 --> 01:06:53,342
Jadi lagi.

835
01:06:55,011 --> 01:06:57,763
Kenapalah nasib aku begini?

836
01:07:36,510 --> 01:07:39,388
{\an8}Hebat betul awak menari tadi.

837
01:07:39,472 --> 01:07:42,141
{\an8}<i>Ada pelatih bunuh diri. Peminat naik gila.</i>

838
01:07:42,224 --> 01:07:43,517
{\an8}Biar saya siasat.

839
01:07:43,601 --> 01:07:44,769
{\an8}<i>- Loanne…</i>
- Hei!

840
01:07:44,852 --> 01:07:46,854
{\an8}Jangan susahkan orang. Balik sajalah.

841
01:07:46,937 --> 01:07:49,523
{\an8}<i>Mereka tak suka berkawan dengan dia.</i>

842
01:07:49,607 --> 01:07:51,108
{\an8}Telefon dia tiada di situ.

843
01:07:51,192 --> 01:07:52,526
{\an8}<i>Awak rasa dia dibunuh?</i>

844
01:07:52,610 --> 01:07:54,111
{\an8}<i>Jom tangkap pelakunya.</i>

845
01:07:54,195 --> 01:07:55,237
{\an8}<i>Awak kenal Loanne?</i>

846
01:07:55,321 --> 01:07:56,822
{\an8}<i>- Siapa awak?</i>
<i>- Awak wartawan?</i>

847
01:07:56,906 --> 01:07:58,699
{\an8}<i>Macam mana awak masuk? Jom.</i>

848
01:07:58,783 --> 01:08:00,326
{\an8}<i>Saya dengar bunyi telefon.</i>

849
01:08:02,203 --> 01:08:03,829
{\an8}<i>Tak pernah dengar nada dering itu.</i>

850
01:08:05,164 --> 01:08:10,044
{\an8}Terjemahan sari kata oleh Aizat Bahri

